      "title": "Protest underway at Galle Fort",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A large number of protesters have been protesting at the Galle Fort where the second Test cricket match between Australia and Sri Lanka is being held at the Galle International Cricket Ground.",
        "Protesters launched a protest march from Galle Town and currently protesting at the Galle Fort urging the President and the government to resign."
